description:
&lt;p&gt;Our wonderful Women&#39;s Health and Maternity Department are looking for a Patient Services Administrator for 15 hours per week on a 12 month fixed term vacancy to cover maternity leave.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This patient-facing role encompasses a variety of daily tasks, including manning the reception desk, answering patient enquiries and processing referrals and appointment bookings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a key member of the Maternity and Women&#39;s Health teams, the successful candidate will have excellent customer service skills and a strong attention to detail. This role involves being the first point of contact with the department for patients, visitors and colleagues and therefore setting a welcoming and professional tone for their further experiences in the unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please contact Jacopo Brancatelli the Validator and Admin Team Leader on jacopo.brancatelli@hhft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
